	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. P.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod a multis diebus nihil a me acceperis nec tuis responderim, excuses me, rogo; scis enim, in hoc bellorum tumultu quibus occupationibus detinear.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsit mihi <persName ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName> noster misitque pro te ea, que hic reperies.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Novi aliud nihil habeo ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName>, nisi quod <persName type="auto_name">Caesar</persName> omnino cogitat de filio in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> promovendo; expectatur singulis horis in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l640" cert="high">Flandria</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitia sunt dilata, ut scis, credo; principes nobis multa de sua constantia promittunt, utinam ita sit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed cum videam illos capite et nervis belli carere, timeo tecum illorum tam frequentes conventus.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Apud nos arma ubique et spes in... ille... fuit cum rege pro pace vel induciis impetrandis; sed statim sensimus Caesaris artes; ita re infetca remisus et iam est in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l640" cert="high">Flandria</placeName> cum suo Caesare, qui ei papatum promittit.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluto dominos et te unice.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, vir optime.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Soloturo</placeName> 24a ap[rilis].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus semper <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8296" cert="high">Bassefontaneus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bulingero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
